Package me.tazadejava.statstracker

Class EnhancedStatsTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.tazadejava.statstracker.EnhancedStatsTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StatsTracker
    public class EnhancedStatsTracker
extends java.lang.Object
implements StatsTracker
    Enhanced stats tracker that builds off of the StreamlinedStatsTracker to give data useful for a recommendation system. Removes some tracked data from the streamlined stats tracker that is not useful for a recommendation system, such as the blocks around the player (LineOfSight)
